Package: glmGraph
Title: Graphical models with Generalised Linear Model (GLM)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jackson", "Kwok", email = "kcf.jackson@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Felix", "Leung", role = c("aut"))
  )
Description: This package provides functions to simulate from and fit graphical models 
    where all conditional distributions follow the generalised linear model. This is 
    mainly used to construct an approximation of multivariate distribution.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.3.3)
Imports:
    VGAM,
    igraph,
    purrr,
    magrittr,
    dplyr
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
